A vast, glowing network of interconnected nodes floating in a neon-lit digital void, each node represented by a small luminescent cube pulsing with electric blue and magenta light. Thin laser-like connection lines weave between hundreds of these cubes, creating an intricate web that stretches toward the horizon. The perspective is from within the network, looking outward as the grid curves and bends like a digital constellation. Rain-slicked chrome surfaces reflect the ambient glow below, while holographic data streams cascade upward like reverse waterfalls. The atmosphere is dense with particle effects and volumetric fog in deep purples and teals. Cyberpunk style with a sense of infinite connectivity and accessibility, conveying the feeling of reaching anyone within a massive technological ecosystem at the speed of light.
